name: Cifoescoliosis
description:
Un día te desayunas con que tu espalda no va mas, 
otra mañana te afeitan, te meten en un quirófano y te mandan al inframundo por 10 horas.
Abren, cortan, trituran, raspan, esparcen, acomodan, perforan, ajustan, cosen y drenan. 
Luego, vida normal, llena de nuevas sensaciones.


One day you discover that your back is wrong 
Another morning they shave you, put you in an operating room and send you to the underworld for 10 hours.
They open, cut, shred, scrape, spread, set, pierce, fit, sew and drain.
Then normal life, full of new sensations.
